ewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-square-terminal size-3.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"m7 11 2-2-2-2"}],["path",{"d":"M11 13h4"}],["rect",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y":"3","rx":"2","ry":"2"}]],["SPAN",{"class":"truncate"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-medium text-primary"},"/","skill:canvas-design"],["SPAN",{"class":"ml-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground"},"Create beautiful visual art in .png and .pdf documents using design philosophy. You should use this skill when the user asks to create a poster, piece of art, design, or other static piece. Create original visual designs, never copying existing artists' work to avoid copyright violations."]]],["BUTTON",{"type":"button","class":"flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-left text-sm transition-colors my-0.5 hover:bg-muted"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-square-terminal size-3.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"m7 11 2-2-2-2"}],["path",{"d":"M11 13h4"}],["rect",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y":"3","rx":"2","ry":"2"}]],["SPAN",{"class":"truncate"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-medium text-primary"},"/","skill:capture-dashboard"],["SPAN",{"class":"ml-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground"},"Capture authenticated dashboards as screenshots and/or HTML using cookie-based authentication. Use when you need to archive dashboard content, take screenshots of authenticated web applications, document web interfaces, or capture dynamic web pages that require login. Supports same-origin crawling up to 2 levels deep with automatic safety filters to avoid logout/delete actions."]]],["BUTTON",{"type":"button","class":"flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-left text-sm transition-colors my-0.5 hover:bg-muted"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-square-terminal size-3.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"m7 11 2-2-2-2"}],["path",{"d":"M11 13h4"}],["rect",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y":"3","rx":"2","ry":"2"}]],["SPAN",{"class":"truncate"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-medium text-primary"},"/","skill:chat-reset-management"],["SPAN",{"class":"ml-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground"},"Interactive guide for configuring and managing chat session resets in Moltbot/Clawdbot AI agents. Use when - (1) Setting up session reset policies, daily resets, or idle timeouts for chatbots, (2) Troubleshooting token limit exceeded, context rot, slow responses, or session-related issues, (3) Optimizing token usage and context management for high-volume DMs or group chats, (4) Configuring auto-compaction, per-peer scoping, or fresh sessions for sensitive tasks, (5) Implementing best practices for session hygiene and monitoring. ALWAYS use when configuring new Moltbot/Clawdbot instances, deploying agents, or debugging session performance. Related - session management, chatbot configuration, token optimization, context limits, session timeout, idle timeout, daily reset, auto-compaction, DM workflow, group chat settings, Moltbot config, Clawdbot setup, session monitoring."]]],["BUTTON",{"type":"button","class":"flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-left text-sm transition-colors my-0.5 hover:bg-muted"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-square-terminal size-3.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"m7 11 2-2-2-2"}],["path",{"d":"M11 13h4"}],["rect",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y":"3","rx":"2","ry":"2"}]],["SPAN",{"class":"truncate"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-medium text-primary"},"/","skill:chrome-cdp"],["SPAN",{"class":"ml-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground"},"Interact with local Chrome browser session using DevTools Protocol. Use when: automating browser tasks, taking screenshots, extracting page data, navigating tabs, or debugging web pages in the user's live Chrome session."]]],["BUTTON",{"type":"button","class":"flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-left text-sm transition-colors my-0.5 hover:bg-muted"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-square-terminal size-3.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"m7 11 2-2-2-2"}],["path",{"d":"M11 13h4"}],["rect",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y":"3","rx":"2","ry":"2"}]],["SPAN",{"class":"truncate"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-medium text-primary"},"/","skill:context7-docs"],["SPAN",{"class":"ml-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground"},"Fetch up-to-date documentation from Context7 for a library. Use when you need current API syntax, code examples, or official documentation for any library or framework."]]],["BUTTON",{"type":"button","class":"flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-left text-sm transition-colors my-0.5 hover:bg-muted"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-square-terminal size-3.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"m7 11 2-2-2-2"}],["path",{"d":"M11 13h4"}],["rect",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y